                            <comment id="13526167" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 7 Dec 2012 06:15:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m pretty sure the first part of getAllLocalAddresses (the getAllByName list) will be a subset of the ones seen by getNetworkInterfaces&apos; addresses.  (We do this in CFRR too &amp;#8211; would make sense to extract it somewhere.)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Otherwise +1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13526245" author="slebresne" created="Fri, 7 Dec 2012 09:16:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You&apos;re right, the getAllByName part is probably useless. I&apos;ve move the getNetworkInterfaces part in FBUtilities (and used it in CFRR and UUIDGen) and committed. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
